\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Then it was back to normal. Always back to normal. He didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t like God\u8217\'92s Eye burgeons because of that. It was like giving a beggar a Lord\u8217\'92s feast and the kicking him out on street again. Seb thought it was better to starve. Get a taste of enlightenment and then be robbed of it is no good.}
